    "The dimensions of the image transferred from the input level and the output values obtained from each level are different from each other.",
    "For this, a widening is applied to the data obtained from the lower levels.",
    "The difference between the expanded images and the input image is calculated in Dif N blocks.",
    "The calculated difference value and the image of this value are transferred to the F n block.",
    "This situation is expressed by Eq."
